Kevin Johnson is the Deans dean of the UC Davis School of Law.  He was appointed 20080515. He is the author of How Did You Get to Be Mexican and Opening the Floodgates: Why America Needs to Rethink its Borders and Immigration Laws.

The law school Kevin Johnson is not the same as the wiki:wikipedia:Kevin Johnson basketball star Kevin Johnson. He is also not any of the wiki:wikipedia:Kevin Johnson (disambiguation) other Kevin Johnsons you may have heard of.
